15 10–104.2.
16 (A) AN APPLICANT FOR A LICENSE ISSUED IN ACCORDANCE WITH §
17 10–103(B) OF THIS SUBTITLE OR UNDER § 10–104, § 10–104.1, OR § 10–106 OF THIS
18 SUBTITLE OR § 10–404 OF THIS TITLE SHALL INCLUDE IN THE APPLICATION
19 DOCUMENTATION VERIFYING THAT THE APPLICANT COMPLETED:
