12 (I) submit to the Commission an application on the form that the
13 Commission provides; AND
14 (II) INCLUDE IN THE APPLICATION DOCUMENTATION
15 VERIFYING THAT THE APPLICANT COMPLETED A HUMAN TRAFFICKING AWARENESS
16 TRAINING IN ACCORDANCE WITH § 10–104.2 OF THIS SUBTITLE.
17 (2) The Commission may renew the for–hire driver’s license by appropriate
18 endorsement on the license.
